body.name: Maupvit Large Shoe Cabinet with 4 Flip Drawers, Freestanding Shoe Organizer with Metal Drawer Bracket for Entryway, Narrow Shoe Rack Cabinet, 5 Sturdy Legs, Rustic Brown
features: 【Entryway Shoe Cabinet】: The hidden shoe storage cabinet with 4 flip doors, stylish and simple rustic brown makes it a neat and beautiful finish and looks great in many different home styles. Perfect for placing in the entryway, hallway, living room, or porch, provides a neat looking in your home and space saving.

【Flip Drawers Shoe Cabinet】: The modern freestanding shoe cabinet adopts the design of space-saving flip drawers, which is easy to open and close. Compared with ordinary shoe racks, this narrow shoe cabinet can be placed in a narrow space, keeping your shoes away from dust and preventing pets from biting your shoes.

【Large Capacity Shoe Cabinet】: The drawer shoe cabinet can store up to 32-40 pairs. There are 4 upper and lower drawers, each drawer contains two layers of storage space. The panel can be adjusted or removed in two grooves to accommodate different heights and sizes of flats, mid boots or heels! Slippers or sweeping robots can be placed on the bottom. There is a fence on the top, ideal for placing potted plants, ornaments, socks and keys, without worrying about falling.

【Safe and Reliable Quality】: This slim shoe cabinet contains an anti-tipping device, which can be fixed on the wall to prevent tipping and protect children's safety. Made of high-quality MDF wood and metal legs, the stable structure ensures super load-bearing capacity. The black metal handle is simple and elegant, feels comfortable, and prevents scratches and injuries during use. 5 Sturdy wooden legs prevent the floor from being scratched, and can be easily cleaned with a damp cloth.

【Amazing After-Sales Service】: With a 48-month warranty, our products are so confident! If there is any problem in logistics and transportation, even if the wood board causes 1mm damage, we are willing to replace it for you for free! Just contact us and we will give you a satisfactory answer within 24 hours.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Discrete shoe storage, easy to assemble.
reviews.reviewText: This was a great purchase. It’s not too wide so it fits nicely in our main hallway. It took some time to build but the instructions were very easy to read and follow. My only word of warning is for large shoes and steel toes. Both my husband and I need steel toes for work he wears a 13, they did not fit into the drawers not even mine. Each drawer has 2 levels, I took the top board out of one of the bottom drawers so it was only one level and the steel toes and my husband’s monster shoes fit in just fine. Glad I got the 4 door one and not the 2 door. Very pleased with the purchase. It looks great and we are using it daily.
